by the way level 34 and dont think I will get much more pp resources from alts for some time.  Armor is good though not need to upgrade soon me thinks so focused on taunt and damage (yayayay) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uxaaxdaleezard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xaax Da Leezard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/25/02 9:15:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1668.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.home.net/eq-jestar/lizard1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Have Wrapped Entropy Spine question</span><hr size=1> <br>
I went on a bit of a weapon-buying spree a few days ago; and although I had never intended on actively obtaining a Wrapped Entropy Spine (I have heard many horror stories about using these), it got thrown into the deal I was making.<br>
<br>
However, instead of passing it on to my warrior, I gave it to my twink SK instead (he was easier to pass the weapon to, and I was just going to test it before passing it on to the warrior); and I have observed that: it does help hold aggro, it seems to proc a lot, and only 2 times out of say 100 did it seem to make the mob run off.<br>
<br>
Based on the other weapons I have on the warrior (not uber but decent), I think I will leave the spine with the SK.  At least if the mob runs off, I have a chance to snare it with Darkness before it gets too far.  I'm still not sure if it would be a good warrior weapon (ratio and delay are decent, as is the AC and taunt factor)... I'd sure hate the mob to run off unexpectedly in close quarters when no one in the group is expecting it.  Just my 2cp after a few days of playing with one. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uvaloren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Valoren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/25/02 12:35:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1668.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://exodusfromchaos.freeservers.com/signatures/valoren_small.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Have Wrapped Entropy Spine question</span><hr size=1> I wield a warrped entrophy serpent spine in my offhand with my main being bloodpoint.  I have noticed that the proc combination and the speed of this combo is great for taunt but the downside being that the spine has been known to cause mobs to be feared on occasion.<br>
<br>
I have had the sperpent spine for about 3 months and have noticed something.  In the last few weeks I have not seen a mob run off using the serpent spine.  This is the only combo I use to any extent but I think the fleeeing may have either been changed or broken.....of course that is speculation only. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ujestarspineripper.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jestar Spineripper</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/25/02 7:36:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1668.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.home.net/eq-jestar/sig1.jpeg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Have Wrapped Entropy Spine question</span><hr size=1> <br>
